{"tid":1466933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試下反向推演","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:17.000Z","uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02ce46001e32e8b69c492d4e8908accc15349976","tid":1466933,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"請大家重讀一次烈士遺命:<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D-Rc2-RU8AEyogM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD-Rc2-RU8AEyogM.jpg&h=79409fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">... 抗爭時間久了 ... 一定要堅持下去。 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n已經有人提示, 就算出坦克車, 64 重演, 中共撕破面皮反檯,<br />\n<br />\n全世界都只係會口頭譴責。 出兵打大陸? 無可能。<br />\n制裁? maybe. <br />\n但香港會被一國一制。<br />\n<br />\n但係對於攬炒派嚟講, 呢個先係最佳結局。<br />\n既然係咁, 試下由呢個角度出發推演:<br />\n<br />\n出坦克嘅原因得一個, 就係運動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">持續</span></span></strong></span>到一個地步, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">動搖共產黨政權。</span></span></strong><br />\n一日你班暴徒做唔到呢點, 佢都只係當你幫佢R痕。<br />\n<br />\n你班友今日阻旅客、用私刑, 林鄭真係會忍唔住笑出嚟。<br />\n因為再咁落去, 成個運動一定散!!! 係自己散!<br />\n<br />\n所以請唔該, 大家用最清醒嘅意志, 提醒自己點樣做好每一步。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/fd/7b/fb/fd7bfb848297c0200a542b1f5e4ac015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Ffd%2F7b%2Ffb%2Ffd7bfb848297c0200a542b1f5e4ac015.jpg&h=8b4ef87d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebbb0bb0deb0fd4f557c6567b527fee176f0293c","tid":1466933,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">梁天琦致香港人的信：<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">懇請不要被仇恨支配自己</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦致香港人的信/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3